ukemia\">plasma_cell_leukemia</a></td><td>Plasmacelle leukæmi</td><td>Plasma cell leukemia / Plasmacelle leukæmi</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-Complications.html#Complications-uremia_clinically\">uremia_clinically</a></td><td>Uræmi (klinisk betydende)</td><td>Uremia (clinically significant) / Uræmi (klinisk betydende)</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-Complications.html#Complications-uremia_dialysis\">uremia_dialysis</a></td><td>Uræmi (kronisk dialysekrævende)</td><td>Uremia (chronic dialysis requiring) / Uræmi (kronisk dialysekrævende)</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-Complications.html#Complications-amyloidosis\">amyloidosis</a></td><td>Amyloidose</td><td>Amyloidosis / Amyloidose / SNOMED-CT: 17602002</td></tr></table></li></ul></div>"
